{"tid":2206491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎耀祥成日問人哋有幾多個十年，涉嫌煽惑他人睇中共禁片","createTime":"2020-09-17T13:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T14:25:52.000Z","uid":229502,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ab95aeebd231b4a74d3c0ecd39811ce7b58f16e1","tid":2206491,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUdo8KA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUdo8KA.png&h=c9e31063&s={SIZE}\" /> TVB染黃真係好嚴重!! 除咗劇組，原來連偽人黎耀祥都係黃屍，記者之前問佢點睇国安法，佢竟然答冇乜留意!? 諗諗吓<strong><span class=\"red\">佢成日重提老掉牙嘅「人生有幾多個十年」，不斷提及祖国禁片，想食盡兩家茶禮賺人仔?</span></strong> 我呸！我唔會再睇YCTVB，更加唔會睇你套雙祥見! <strong><span class=\"red\">屌你老味嬲嬲地, 派埋嬲比你啲廣告商<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DGWFrLy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDGWFrLy.jpg&h=c24e14e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n            十年？你終於露出狐狸尾巴！<br />\n <p class=\"center\">【每日任務@ 17 Sep】 💎 正官庄 💎 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ckjhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fckjhk%2F&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=30232f2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ckjhk/</a> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6ZLCca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6ZLCca.png&h=00de224b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n</p> 正官庄係三料廣告商，首先呢兩年都有喺TVB賣廣告；第二搵咗戲裡戲外都跋扈囂張嘅黎耀祥（A.K.A.韓信）嚟代言；第三喺Big Big Shop寄賣。 黎耀祥金句： 「經常鬧TVB的人，我覺得沒有良心」、「我真係唔信你細個無睇過電視，到今時今日大個，巴閉喇，讀咗書喇，知識分子搵到錢喇，中產喇，飲杯咖啡睇法國電影喇，就話呢啲（劇集）好膠喇」 ============================================ [quote]<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">【抵制 TVB戰線】</span></span></strong> Follow 抵制TVB戰線，每日派嬲，對方廣告費就億億聲咁跌！ <span class=\"x-large\"> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno4tvb%2F&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=66434878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/</a> </span></p>"},{"pid":"449ea70698d729cac3899448f4667f8262056a3b","tid":2206491,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1f0f8dfe063b0f9c4bb9ea0c22a8199f7c2980","tid":2206491,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3edf8facae348a33c63fb959adeab421d85d789","tid":2206491,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75302e9b65992601e5b6e438f94bb5eeb07318c6","tid":2206491,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e27cf2d243f19fff98dd0e2d56fbfd67d9c5dd9","tid":2206491,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"449ea70698d729cac3899448f4667f8262056a3b","tid":2206491,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f407b9a3b251e66d6bad6ffb78473609aaa56f5","tid":2206491,"uid":271497,"